{"id":172756,"type":2,"name":"降龙记","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1c/72/172756_4YYiV.jpg","summary":"　　六十年代第一春，在某里弄版的工厂里，工人们立志炼出特种钢，忽然一根钢条从地上跳起，变成一条黑龙，他嘲笑里弄小厂搞尖端是妄想。工人们用铁钳将他夹住，黑龙进行挣扎，经过一场激战，黑龙被降服。紧接着，工人们土洋结合、大闹技术革命，实现了生产自动化，炼出了特种钢","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/15676\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万古蟾</a>、<a href=\"/person/22163\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">岳路</a>、<a href=\"/person/22239\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">陈正鸿</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/22204\">段时俊</a></li><li><span>设定: </span><a href=\"/person/22198\">詹同渲</a>、梁力克、俞士龙</li><li><span>制作: </span><a href=\"/person/7499\">上海美术电影制片厂</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1960</li><li><span>脚本: </span>集体</li>","collection":{"collect":2,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"中国","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":913442,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/913442","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":22163,"image":"","name":"岳路","desc":"导演"},{"id":22239,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b2/52/22239_prsn_cdybF.jpg","name":"陈正鸿","desc":"导演"},{"id":15676,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a0/fe/15676_prsn_6A9N0.jpg","name":"万嘉淇","desc":"导演"},{"id":22204,"image":"","name":"段时俊","desc":"音乐"},{"id":22198,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f3/6c/22198_prsn_0ZJmS.jpg","name":"詹同渲","desc":"设定"},{"id":7499,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1e/b5/7499_prsn_M4v1M.jpg","name":"上海美术电影制片厂","desc":"制作"}]}